{"tid":1373853,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"帶住爸爸媽媽遊行既人同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:35:36.000Z","uid":140540,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54ac242dbd583ef43d48b7b3381ee820504da26e","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"今日見到有個帶曬裝備既勇武仔想入前線，但後面佢爸爸一直跟住佢，個勇武仔係咁叫佢爸爸走，唔好跟埋去，佢地兩個都眼泛淚光個一幕真係好感動！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但唔該係咁既情怳下，麻煩帶你爸爸一齊走！你爸爸都係擔心你唔想你有事，香港有我地救，麻煩保護好自己保護好自己既家人，唔好咁任性，我唔想睇到大家出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n今日大家都辛苦啦，大家今日都好勇，對催淚彈免疫真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n下次一定會再見，記得保護身邊朋友！"},{"pid":"e430e63c62460844d850ace668b92ee7afcb0f01","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"只係純粹分享下今日見到既故事"},{"pid":"fe0c04599d5224b41e2fcf248a458def81f57ef8","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"記得保護好自己家人，沖係其次"},{"pid":"9b032abc42bfc242c990fa0454d28b79b4694fb6","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"屋企人第一"},{"pid":"af6b2cc31088387ed66e8f1dc9bd1ebbcf72dab6","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"希望你地唔好咁傻"},{"pid":"9431855e4323318997989a032dc7de256392d15d","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人都見到尼一幕呢？"},{"pid":"9cc9a30252821ef031a8faf69059b2d1160a3819","tid":1373853,"uid":140540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"希望佢地父子平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}